{"id":101045,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/温家宝是邓小平理论的忠实捍卫者/","date":"2010-08-27T17:13:38Z","modified":"2015-12-22T02:59:42Z","title":"温家宝是邓小平理论的忠实捍卫者","content":"<p><p><span>中共中央政治局常委、国务院总理温家宝最近在中国大陆深圳特区成立卅周年前夕到深圳考察，除了继续强调“坚定不移地推进改革开放”外，还罕见地谈及了政治体制改革。他强调，改革不能停滞倒退，否则就是违背人民意志，能是“死路一条”。这番言论引起海内外的极大关注。在第一时间里，笔者也写出《</span><span>温家宝如何定位“深圳大特区”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span><span>》的博文在凤凰网发表。可惜，此文一小时后被网管删除。此后笔者在深圳新闻网和网易博客贴出此文，幸运的是至今还存在。</span></p>\n<p><span>笔者在深圳生活多年，也较长时间在政府部门和官媒中任职，自忖有点儿发言权。</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>是深圳、珠海、汕头、厦门等四大经济特区建立卅周年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>年前，深圳是一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>万人的小渔村，现在 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><strong><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p></span></span></strong><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idangxingdafa.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8882,8800,10951,29704]}